data.description: $5,000 towards Buyers Closing costs. Don't miss the chance to call this spacious one-story residence with No HOA, New AC and 6 year old roof your home! Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths, along with two living areas offering versatile configurations and various entertainment possibilities. The 4th bedroom, which previously served as a Daycare space, features a window that opens to the living area and could  be transformed into a Studio, Video Game Room or Nursery. French doors provide seamless access to the backyard from the second living area. Additionally, the side yard has been paved, offering outdoor storage options or the potential to create an extra entertainment area. Ideally situated just minutes away from JBSA-Lackland and Medina, and with convenient access to 1604 and 90, this beautiful one-story house is waiting for you to make it your own.
